<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="scroll-smooth">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Sidewayz 8 Solutions | AI-Powered Creative Technology Studio</title>
<meta name="description" content="Sidewayz 8 Solutions is a New Orleans-based AI-powered creative technology studio building practical, revenue-driven digital products, SaaS platforms, and AI automation tools.">
<meta name="robots" content="index, follow">
