<section id="hero" class="relative w-full h-screen overflow-hidden">
<canvas id="hero-canvas"></canvas>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-sidewayz-dark/40 to-sidewayz-dark z-10"></div>
<div class="relative z-20 w-full h-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center px-6">
<div class="text-center max-w-6xl mx-auto">
<div class="hero-eyebrow opacity-0 mb-8">
<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 border border-copper/30 rounded-full text-xs font-mono tracking-[0.3em] text-copper uppercase">
<span class="w-2 h-2 bg-copper rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
AI-Powered Creative Technology Studio
</span>
</div>
<h1 class="hero-title opacity-0 font-display font-black text-5xl sm:text-7xl md:text-8xl lg:text-9xl tracking-tight leading-[0.9] mb-10">
<span class="block text-white">SIDEWAYZ</span>
<span class="block text-gradient text-copper-glow">8</span>
</h1>
<p class="hero-tagline opacity-0 font-accent italic text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl text-white/80 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 leading-relaxed">We build solutions for a sidewayz world.</p>
<div class="hero-cta opacity-0 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
<a href="#products" class="magnetic-btn px-8 py-4 bg-copper text-sidewayz-dark font-display font-bold text-sm tracking-wider rounded-full hover:bg-copper-light transition-all relative z-10">EXPLORE PRODUCTS</a>
<a href="#contact" class="magnetic-btn px-8 py-4 border border-white/30 text-white font-display font-bold text-sm tracking-wider rounded-full hover:border-copper hover:text-copper transition-all relative z-10">START A PROJECT</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="absolute bottom-12 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
<span class="text-xs tracking-[0.3em] text-white/40 uppercase font-mono">Scroll</span>
<div class="w-px h-16 bg-gradient-to-b from-copper to-transparent"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="absolute top-1/4 left-10 w-2 h-2 bg-copper rounded-full animate-float opacity-60"></div>
<div class="absolute top-1/3 right-20 w-3 h-3 bg-neon rounded-full animate-float opacity-40" style="animation-delay:1s"></div>
<div class="absolute bottom-1/3 left-1/4 w-2 h-2 bg-neon-pink rounded-full animate-float opacity-50" style="animation-delay:2s"></div>
</section>

<section id="stats" class="relative w-full py-16 lg:py-20 border-y border-white/5 bg-sidewayz-darker/50">
<div class="w-full px-6 lg:px-12">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
<div class="text-center lg:text-left"><div class="font-display font-black text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-gradient mb-2 counter-value" data-target="9">0</div><div class="text-white/40 text-xs tracking-[0.2em] uppercase font-mono">Products Live</div></div>
<div class="text-center lg:text-left"><div class="font-display font-black text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-copper mb-2 counter-value" data-target="6" data-suffix="+">0</div><div class="text-white/40 text-xs tracking-[0.2em] uppercase font-mono">Industries</div></div>
<div class="text-center lg:text-left"><div class="font-display font-black text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-neon mb-2 counter-value" data-target="4" data-suffix="+">0</div><div class="text-white/40 text-xs tracking-[0.2em] uppercase font-mono">Software Directories</div></div>
<div class="text-center lg:text-left"><div class="font-display font-black text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-neon-pink mb-2 counter-value" data-target="1">0</div><div class="text-white/40 text-xs tracking-[0.2em] uppercase font-mono">Sister Brand</div></div>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<section id="about" class="relative w-full py-32 lg:py-48 overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/2 h-full bg-gradient-to-l from-copper/5 to-transparent"></div>
<div class="absolute -bottom-32 -left-32 w-96 h-96 bg-neon/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
<div class="relative z-10 w-full px-6 lg:px-12">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
<div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-24 items-start mb-24">
<div class="reveal-left">
<span class="text-copper text-sm font-mono tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4 block">About Us</span>
<h2 class="font-display font-black text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-white leading-tight">BUILDING PRACTICAL,<br/><span class="text-gradient">REVENUE-DRIVEN</span><br/>DIGITAL PRODUCTS</h2>
</div>
<div class="reveal-right lg:pt-12 space-y-6">
<p class="text-lg text-white/70 leading-relaxed">Sidewayz 8 Solutions is a multidisciplinary technology and creative studio focused on building practical, revenue-driven digital products. We operate at the intersection of software development, artificial intelligence, branding, and design — turning ideas into scalable, real-world solutions.</p>
<p class="text-white/50 leading-relaxed">We design, build, and launch platforms that solve concrete problems for individuals, startups, and small businesses. From AI-powered web applications to branding systems and automation tools, our work is rooted in usability, performance, and measurable outcomes.</p>
<p class="text-white/50 leading-relaxed">Founded on the belief that technology should be accessible, efficient, and purpose-built — not bloated, over-engineered, or disconnected from real needs. We move quickly, iterate intelligently, and focus on shipping products that work.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="section-line mb-24"></div>
<div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
<div class="reveal-left">
<span class="text-copper text-sm font-mono tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4 block">Our Mission</span>
<h3 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-white mb-8">Building smart, efficient digital solutions</h3>
<ul class="space-y-4">
<li class="flex items-start gap-4"><div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-copper/20 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1"><div class="w-2 h-2 bg-copper rounded-full"></div></div><span class="text-white/70">Simplify complex problems through thoughtful technology</span></li>
<li class="flex items-start gap-4"><div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-neon/20 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1"><div class="w-2 h-2 bg-neon rounded-full"></div></div><span class="text-white/70">Create tools that deliver immediate, tangible value</span></li>
<li class="flex items-start gap-4"><div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-neon-purple/20 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1"><div class="w-2 h-2 bg-neon-purple rounded-full"></div></div><span class="text-white/70">Bridge the gap between creativity and engineering</span></li>
<li class="flex items-start gap-4"><div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-neon-pink/20 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1"><div class="w-2 h-2 bg-neon-pink rounded-full"></div></div><span class="text-white/70">Empower users with systems that are intuitive, scalable, and reliable</span></li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="reveal-right">
<div class="relative p-8 lg:p-12 bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/10 rounded-3xl">
<div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-copper/5 to-transparent rounded-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
<div class="relative z-10">
<div class="text-6xl text-copper/20 font-accent mb-6">"</div>
<blockquote class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-white/90 italic leading-relaxed mb-6 font-accent">Technology should be accessible, efficient, and purpose-built — not bloated, over-engineered, or disconnected from real needs.</blockquote>
<footer class="text-copper font-medium font-mono text-sm tracking-wider">— The Sidewayz Philosophy</footer>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<section id="products" class="relative w-full py-32 lg:py-48 overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-sidewayz-dark via-sidewayz-darker to-sidewayz-dark"></div>
<div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-copper/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
<div class="relative z-10 w-full px-6 lg:px-12">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
<div class="text-center mb-20">
<span class="reveal-up text-copper text-sm font-mono tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4 block">What We Build</span>
<h2 class="reveal-up font-display font-black text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-white mb-6">OUR <span class="text-gradient">PRODUCTS</span></h2>
<p class="reveal-up text-white/50 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg">Innovative solutions built with passion, powered by AI, designed for impact.</p>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
  <div class="flip-card reveal-up group" onclick="this.classList.toggle('flipped')">
    <div class="flip-card-inner">
      <div class="flip-card-front p-8 relative">
        <div class="product-badge bg-copper/20 text-copper">AI Powered</div>
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-copper/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-copper/30 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-copper" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl text-white mb-3">Smart ATS Resume</h3>
        <p class="text-white/60 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">A resume builder specifically designed to beat company ATS and get your resume back in human hands.</p>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <span class="text-xs font-mono text-white/30">Featured on 4+ software directories</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flip-hint">Tap to flip</div>
      </div>
